snippet.title: Overboss - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Become a villain in this retro-inspired board game. Draft terrain tiles, recruit monsters, build your dungeon, and become the OVERBOSS. 
Available on August 15th on PC and consoles!

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2109390/Overboss/
